{"type":"text","timestamp":1775877439530,"sessionID":"ses_28575e89bffehzHcfjM9TrjAPT","part":{"id":"prt_d7a8b34a9001YklfMCsg10ElPO","messageID":"msg_d7a8b1fdc001OyO72ifkWDgizP","sessionID":"ses_28575e89bffehzHcfjM9TrjAPT","type":"text","text":"Done! Created `proposal_ar_029.md` for the AgentCube project with:\n\n- **Purpose**: HTTP 底层客户端实现，支撑 SDK 与控制平面和数据平面的通信\n- **Scope**: 控制平面客户端、数据平面客户端、工具模块、异常层次结构、配置解析\n- **Impact Analysis**: 依赖关系（requests/PyJWT/cryptography）、模块依赖图、向后兼容性、测试影响\n- **Alternatives Considered**: httpx vs requests、集中式配置、同步/异步双版本\n- **Implementation Notes**: 超时处理、Session ID 管理、文件上传、错误处理\n- **Success Criteria**: 6 项验收标准","time":{"start":1775877439529,"end":1775877439529}}}
